  "_comment": "Reproducibility contract for the full-game lifted-vmless graph (kegg/graph_full/). Authored by scripts/build_full_graph.py --write-manifest from a pmlift --auto-exclude-waits convergence over KE.EXE. 'graph_eips' is the emitted set = static liftable census - convergence exclusions - authored override EIPs (authored wins). Re-derive exclusions with: pypy dos_re/tools/pmlift.py --exe assets/KE.EXE --auto-entries 5000 --emit-graph <dir> --verify --steps 80000000 --auto-exclude-waits 20",
